  "body": "### Regressions\r\n- [x] Behavior of navigation view when keyboard is opened\r\n- [ ] Chat opening loading screen is incomplete (only loading skeleton is shown, other components will be implemented)\r\n\r\n### Also in develop, should be fixed in the scope of optimization\r\n- [x] Navigation view header is too big for empty chats\r\n- [x] Navigation view flickers when opening chat\r\n- [x] Navigation view title is animated when chat screen is empty\r\n\r\n### Tech debt\r\n- [x] Use `animatedScrollHandler` for flat list\r\n- [ ] Get rid of all reagent atoms in `messages.view.cljs` file (only one left)\r\n- [ ] Rename `scroll-y`\r\n- [ ] `scroll-to-botom-fn` needs improvement (probably should be an event)\r\n- [ ] Remove rnio library\r\n- [ ] Loading skeleton while hot-reloading\r\n\r\n### Design input requires\r\n- [x] `header-container-top-margin` 48 or 52?\r\n- [x] Position of pinned banner for starting animation(currently 142) (UPD: This poistion should be updated later, will depend on new-profile implementation and bio height)\r\n- [x] Position of avatar for starting animation (https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/pull/18055#issuecomment-1849509480)",
